dc_description_s: This data layer represents trails for Sauk County, Wisconsin in 2019. [A trail or path used for walking, cycling, hiking or other form of non-vehicular transportation. In some cases, other forms of motorized transportation may be permitted on a regular or seasonal basis.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: http://data-saukgis.opendata.arcgis.com.
